flowchart TD
    A[Handler Returns Result] --> B{Success or Error?}
    B -- Success --> C[Wrap in data envelope]
    B -- Error --> D[Wrap AppError in error envelope]
    C --> E[Attach meta: requestId, timing]
    D --> E
    E --> F[Serialize JSON]
    F --> G[Set HTTP Status from envelope]
    G --> H[Send Response]
